	(text "Startup-sequence (chronological order from top to bottom):\n1. Battery    Starts: +6V_Buck -> +5V5_bus (Always On with Battery) \n2. 5V5_bus    Starts: MCP1502, +1V8_AVDD and +3V3_DIO\n3.1 3V3_DIO   Starts: ESP32\n3.2 1V8_AVDD  Starts: +5V_Ana.\n4.1 3V3_ESP32 Starts: Sensors\n4.2 +5V_Ana   Starts: OPA2387's, NCV8184\n"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 124.714 -33.782 0)
		(effects
